* ''Letter from Giovanni Faber to Prince Frederico Cesi dated April 13, 1625''. Dans : William B. Carpenter et W. H. Dallinger, éd., ''The Microscope and Its Revelations'', {{8th}} ed. (Philadelphia, Pennsylvania: P. Blakiston's Son & Co., 1901), pages 124-125.

